This binary file is an input storage file containing input messages
for given delivery+region.

The format of the file:
    records one by one

The format of the record (version 1):
    uint16  length of the record in octets not including this field
    uint16  version of the record
    uint64  message id
    uint8   state (see main README), optionally ORed with 0x80 (embed_text_flag)
    uint64  subscriber (see main README)
    cstring userdata
 if embed_text_flag set (see state field above):
    cstring message text
 else:
    uint32  message text id in glossary
